data.description: You are going to absolutely FALL in LOVE with this Stunning Taylor Morrison built BEAUTY! Your meticulously maintained, clean and MOVE-IN ready home awaits with luxury upgrades and a quiet conservation setting! Meet the Arezzo villa home! The Arezzo is 1956 SF with 3 bedrooms, a study + a covered, screened & sunny extended lanai! The open concept shows off designer upgrades unique to this home: SHUTTERS, TRAY CEILINGS, GRANITE countertops, a GLASS entry door, high 9’ ceilings & a 3-door pocket slider in the gathering room. The kitchen features reverse osmosis filtration, stainless steel appliances, a GAS range, panty + generous cabinet and countertop space! The owner’s suite is a comfortable retreat with views of the mature FL landscaping that borders the back yard. The owner’s en suite includes dual sinks, staggered cabinets, an oversized shower + an oversized walk in closet with custom shelving. The updates in this LOVED home includes: 2021 carpeting in bedrooms, 2023 exterior paint, tile roof pressure washed 2023, garage overhead storage system, 2021 water softener, a 30 AMP generator switch, SIMPLISAFE alarm system + a TV antenna in the attic to access 100+ channels! From the moment you enter the gated community of ESPLANADE of TAMPA, you will SEE and FEEL the difference this QUALITY community offers- meticulously maintained lawns, FL native landscaping, paver driveways, ponds, top-level clubhouse + amenities catering to executive style homes! This is a beautiful community offering a LIFESTYLE with a resort-like clubhouse, community pool, tennis, pickle ball, shuffleboard, dog park, fire pit and fitness! Come meet your neighbors! This is an active community with holiday gatherings, water aerobics, and game nights! And maybe the best feature is LANDSCAPE maintenance is INCLUDED!  Terrific location in desirable Wesley Chapel! Close to restaurants, shops and I75! This community is NOT a 55+ community- VISIT & TOUR to see and feel the difference of this exclusive ESPLANADE community for ANY age!
